\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The 27-year-old athlete'sgold-winning performance\", \"from\": 264, \"to\": 313}, {\"ngram\": \"the 100m\", \"from\": 317, \"to\": 325}, {\"ngram\": \"last place\", \"from\": 402, \"to\": 412}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the finish line was so closely contested that the runners faced an agonizing wait as officials scrutinized footage of the final seconds, and Lyles himself told Kishane Thompson, 23, that he believed the Jamaican had won.\", \"from\": 483, \"to\": 707, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 628, \"end\": 633, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.9840007524863027, \"rank\": 0.0162095102097472, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\"}, {\"begin\": 655, \"end\": 663, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tina_Thompson\", \"score\": 0.8478324608534589, \"rank\": 0.1794783120252571, \"text\": \"Thompson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tina_Thompson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tina_Thompson\"}, {\"begin\": 690, \"end\": 698, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"score\": 0.9712464758309274, \"rank\": 0.029604765076793136, \"text\": \"Jamaican\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaicans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the finish line\", \"from\": 487, \"to\": 502}, {\"ngram\": \"the runners\", \"from\": 533, \"to\": 544}, {\"ngram\": \"an agonizing wait\", \"from\": 551, \"to\": 568}, {\"ngram\": \"officials\", \"from\": 572, \"to\": 581}, {\"ngram\": \"footage\", \"from\": 594, \"to\": 601}, {\"ngram\": \"the final seconds\", \"from\": 605, \"to\": 622}]}, {\"sen