 \"a 0.178 reaction time\", \"from\": 936, \"to\": 957}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When told that statistic after the race by a journalist, Lyles said: \\\"Slowest reaction time-that's crazy!\", \"from\": 990, \"to\": 1095, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1047, \"end\": 1052, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.9840007524863027, \"rank\": 0.0162095102097472, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that statistic\", \"from\": 1000, \"to\": 1014}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 1021, \"to\": 1029}, {\"ngram\": \"a journalist\", \"from\": 1033, \"to\": 1045}, {\"ngram\": \"Slowest reaction time\", \"from\": 1060, \"to\": 1081}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I thought I was a little better than that but that goes to prove that reaction time does not win races.\\\"\", \"from\": 1096, \"to\": 1200, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"reaction time\", \"from\": 1166, \"to\": 1179}, {\"ngram\": \"races\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1198}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The slow start looked as if it had destroyed his chances, and he was still trailing in last place some 40 meters in.\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1318, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The slow start\", \"from\": 1202, \"to\": 1216}, {\"ngram\": \"his chances\", \"from\": 1247, \"to\": 1258}, {\"ngram\": \"last place\", \"from\": 1289, \"to\": 1299}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But expert analysis of the race reveals how Lyles managed to pick up speed as the finish line approached.\", \"from\": 1320, \"to\": 1425, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1364, \"end\": 1369, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jordan_Lyles\", \"score\": 0.9840007524863027, \"rank\": 0.0162095102097472, \"text\": \"Lyles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://